: {"text": "深圳新能源车指标申请条件调整 取消社保限制 深圳市交通运输局发布《关于调整新能源小汽车增量指标申请条件的通告》，通告透露，将取消非深户籍人员申请新能源小汽车增量指标社保限制。放宽名下仅有 1 辆在深圳市登记的小汽车个人申请混合动力小汽车增量指标的条件限制。根据现行的《深圳市小汽车增量调控管理实施细则》，这意味着市民只需要持居住证，即可申请新能源小汽车增量指标。而已有 1 辆粤 B 牌的个人，还可以再申请购买 1 辆混合动力小汽车。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-8158c2a9a4af214104404c335fce5906_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "195 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/655664261"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIhZyFncys0rAIEAMaCTEwNzk4MDk4NiDq5/uxBjAAOLsDQANyCTY1NTY2NDI2MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1715545128.414642", "card_id": "Q_655597551", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 421}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "丰田汽车发布 2023 财报「营业利润达人民币 2492 亿元，同比飙涨96.4%」，背后原因有哪些？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据日本共同社消息，丰田汽车公司 8 日发布 2023 财年（2023 年 4 月至 2024 年 3 月）合并财报，反映主营业务盈利情况的营业利润较上财年增长 96.4%，达到创纪录的 5.3529 万亿日元（约合人民币 2492 亿元）。日企营业利润站上 5 万亿日元大关尚属首次。中新经纬 - 快报 - 丰田汽车 2023 年利润增 96.4%"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-896ef3a564ef72aaaf211764ef416a7c_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "175 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/655597551"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIhZyFncys0rAIEAMaCTEwNzk2NjAxMCD2lfixBjAAOIwIQARyCTY1NTU5NzU1MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1715545128.415160", "card_id": "Q_655427237", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 133}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "90 后医生下班摆摊日